                  Release Notes for RoboSim
        --------------------------------------------

************************************************************

Version 1.3.0 - April 15, 2014
	*) added new preconfig options
	*) fixed movexy turning bug
	*) fixed tipping during high speed motion
	*) removed limit of 240 deg/sec

Version 1.2.0 - March 13, 2014
	*) added trackwidth option to all movexy*() functions
	*) recordAngle outputs in degrees not radians
	*) RoboSim GUI allows custom sizing

Version 1.1.0 - March 5, 2014
	*) RoboSim GUI allows the user to specify the size of wheels for a robot
	*) Help menu linking to User's Guide PDF
	*) Correct trackwidth calculation for turning angle computation
	*) fix bug in movexy() which stopped robot from reaching point
	*) new functions: 	movexyExpr
				movexyFunc

Version 1.0.0 - January 8, 2014
	*) The original release
